<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Transaction Rejected</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      padding: 20px;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 30px;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: auto;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    h1 {
      color: #dc3545;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #888;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Transaction Rejected</h1>
    <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
    <p>
      Unfortunately, your transaction with code <strong>{{transactionCode}}</strong> has been <strong>rejected</strong>.
    </p>
    <p>
      If you believe this is a mistake or want to try again, feel free to contact support or make a new transaction.
    </p>
    <p class="footer">
      &copy; {{year}} Your Company. All rights reserved.
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
